define: Use this api to fetch the logistics information of an order, these info can be used for self-design AWB printing. Besides, this api supports returning personal info as images.

error_list.name: error_status
error_list.description: Status verification failed, shipping documents of this package cannot be printed now.

error_list.name: logistics.error_param
error_list.description: The order is being allocated, please wait until the allocate is completed.

error_list.name: error_permission
error_list.description: Sorry you don't have the permission, detail: {msg}.

error_list.name: error_server
error_list.description: Got an error when trying to generate image, please try again

error_list.name: logistics.error_booking_order
error_list.description: This order is matched order with booking, don't need arrange shipment through seller side.

error_list.name: logistics.error_param
error_list.description: You can not get order logistics of warehouse order.

error_list.name: logistics.error_status_limit
error_list.description: The order status is invalid. Please check the order status.

error_list.name: error_channel_unsupport
error_list.description: This logistic channel/logistic type doesn’t support retrieving info from Open API. Please use v2.logistics.download_shipping_document API instead.

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: Not allowed to self design AWB

error_list.name: logistics.package_number_not_exist
error_list.description: Please request with package_number for this split order.

error_list.name: logistics.can_not_print_combine_order
error_list.description: This order is part of a combined parcel, please use Seller Center instead.

error_list.name: logistics.can_not_print_jit_order
error_list.description: This shipping channel only supports document printing in Shopee seller center

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: There is no access_token in query.

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: There is no partner_id in query.

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: There is no sign in query.

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: The information you queried is not found.

error_list.name: error_param
error_list.description: This order logistics is not allowed to get.
